    <div class="consultation-description">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Consultation description</h2>

      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<div class="call-to-action">
<p>Following feedback from our stakeholders, we have extended the deadline for comments to Friday 24 April 2015.</p>
</div>

<p>The VMD has responded to an issue raised by stakeholders during the Red Tape Challenge 2013 agriculture, livestock, animal health and welfare, plant health, bees and forestry regulations theme.</p>

<p>You can submit your views on the consultation on the <a rel="external" href="https://consult.defra.gov.uk/vmd/review-of-approach-to-issuing-an-atc">Defra Citizen Space website</a>.</p>
